sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as Client App
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant Service as Business Service
    participant Databricks as Databricks
    participant Cache as Redis Cache

    Client->>API: POST /api/query
    API->>Auth: Validate Token
    Auth-->>API: Token Valid

    API->>Service: Forward Request
    Service->>Cache: Check Cache
    Cache-->>Service: Cache Miss

    Service->>Databricks: Execute SQL Query
    Note over Service,Databricks: Query executes on SQL Warehouse

    Databricks-->>Service: Query Results

    Service->>Cache: Store in Cache
    Cache-->>Service: Cached

    Service-->>API: Response
    API-->>Client: 200 OK + Data
